{"title":"前缀和与差分","uid":"f65c2271ed43cdf14e2eea3c0c440d44","slug":"前缀和与差分","date":"2021-09-16T12:34:33.000Z","updated":"2021-09-16T12:38:37.371Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/前缀和与差分.json","keywords":null,"cover":null,"content":"<h1 id=\"前缀和\"><a href=\"#前缀和\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"前缀和\"></a>前缀和</h1><h2 id=\"问题引入\"><a href=\"#问题引入\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"问题引入\"></a>问题引入</h2><h3 id=\"给定n个数a1-a2-a3-……an-有m次询问操作-给定l和r-求al-ar的和为多少\"><a href=\"#给定n个数a1-a2-a3-……an-有m次询问操作-给定l和r-求al-ar的和为多少\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"给定n个数a1,a2,a3,……an,有m次询问操作,给定l和r,求al ~ ar的和为多少\"></a>给定n个数a1,a2,a3,……an,有m次询问操作,给定l和r,求al ~ ar的和为多少</h3><p><strong>要想求这个问题,我们需要知道a的前缀和为多少</strong></p>\n<p><strong>$我们令b_1 = a_1,b_2 = a_1 + a_2,b_3 = a_1 + a_2 + a_3,……b_k = a_1 + a_2 + a_3 + …… + a_k;则b_1 ~ b_k 就是a对应的前缀和$</strong></p>\n<h2 id=\"差分\"><a href=\"#差分\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"差分\"></a>差分</h2><ul>\n<li>差分也十分简单</li>\n<li>查分的问题是给定l和r让你求出 l ~ r之间的和</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>显而易见的是</strong>:<br>$a_l ~ a_r的和 = a_1 ~ a_{l - 1}的和 - a_1 ~ a_r的和 = b_r - b_{l - 1}$</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-c++\" data-language=\"c++\"><code class=\"language-c++\">#include &lt;cstdio&gt;\n#include &lt;cstring&gt;\n#include &lt;cstdlib&gt;\n#include &lt;algorithm&gt;\n\nusing namespace std;\n\nconst int maxn &#x3D; 1e6+5;\n\nint n,m,z[maxn],sum[maxn];\n\nint main()\n&#123;\n    scanf(&quot;%d%d&quot;,&amp;n,&amp;m);\n    for(int i &#x3D; 1;i &lt;&#x3D; n)\n        scanf(&quot;%d&quot;,&amp;z[i]);\n    for(int i &#x3D; 1;i &lt;&#x3D; n;i++)\n        sum[i] &#x3D; sum[i-1] + z[i];\n    for(int i &#x3D; 1;i &lt;&#x3D; m;i++)\n    &#123;\n        int l,r;\n        scanf(&quot;%d%d&quot;,&amp;l,&amp;r);\n        printf(&quot;%d\\n&quot;,sum[r] - sum[r-1]);\n    &#125;\n    return 0\n&#125;<span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></